<TEXTAREA NAME="ReplyMessage" ROWS=10 COLS=45 WRAP="VIRTUAL">[QUOTE]Originally posted by Tundar:
[B]Just fyi, there are some short names:

/tar = /target
/ass = /assist
/hot = /hotbutton

I often use /tar if there comes a call for "heal vobarn" in the raidchannel.
Then I just type "/tar voba" and if he's within range I heal him.

Often using:
/stand
/cast 2 (divine light or other fast heal)
/x Divine Light to %T
Where x is number of raidchannel

There is alot of various possibilities that can make you say things like:
"Healing Niffe the gnome" with this:
"Healing %T the %r"

Check the manual supplement in your EQ directory for more.[/B][/QUOTE]

</TEXTAREA>
